Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=4}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-san}'s smartphone?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.90,0:00:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I need you to locate her. {Hey, Arona. Find my Hoshino}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.99,0:00:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried accessing the GSC's central network,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't identify her location.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.51,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can find some clue.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.47,0:00:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Is that you, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.50,0:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be the right floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you{**, Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.87,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long been eager to\ndiscuss matters directly with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the stories of\nthe GSC's President's enigmatic guest—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.71,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher at the Federal Investigations Club Schale.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, rest assured. {BE NOT AFRAID}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not looking to become your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, we'd prefer the opposite.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.97,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of a tiny school such as Abydos\nis of little consequence to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you—you're a different matter entirely.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the potential to become\nquite a thorn in our side.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.49,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Where are my manners?\nAllow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.58,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Black Suit. I won't mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown rather fond of this name, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.30,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are much like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We, too, originate from outside of Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We simply hail from a different realm than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gematria.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our name.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.36,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the organisation I belong to,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to put it into terms you may be more familiar with. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.57,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission lies in expanding knowledge\nthrough observation, exploration, and experimentation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.74,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite how we appear,\nwe're no more alien than you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But onto the main topic.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be willing to enter into\na partnership with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.67,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You would so readily reject an opportunity\nto unearth the truth behind the mystical?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If not Mystics, what, then, {\i1}are{\i0} you pursuing in Kivotos?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.81,0:05:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is for you to give Hoshino back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.94,0:05:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And what, pray tell, grants you\nthe authority to make such a demand?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} is no longer a student of Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.62,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you haven't overlooked\nthe form submitted by your own student?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I saw her withdrawal form.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is there to argue?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She no longer falls under your purview{**, Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.09,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't signed that form yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.85,0:06:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still part of the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still the vice president of the student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.27,0:06:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's still my precious student.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.44,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're her teacher,\nany official actions necessitate your signature.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather inconvenient.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.78,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You deceived my students.\nYou and your organisation.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.00,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You toyed with their feelings\nand took advantage of their suffering.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.71,0:06:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.42,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If one were to choose between "good" and "evil",\nour actions would unambiguously be considered evil.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil, yes, but well within our rights.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that distinction needs to be made clear.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.18,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we did not cause Abydos's desertification.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.56,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sandstorms were atypical,\nbut not outside the realm of possibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't predict every natural disaster.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Should some people suffer of thirst as a result,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunists will naturally emerge to sell them water.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is simply business as usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.00,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that water is sold at an exorbitant price?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly a rare occurrence.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Such scenarios are commonplace in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who possess exploit those who lack.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Determining one's future is a luxury\nthe weak aren't afforded.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Schale's teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.68,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san}, and in return,\nI will guarantee Abydos's well-being.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.06,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ensure that your students\ncan attend school without worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} would want, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.61,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to believe you,\nthey wouldn't want it to happen like this. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.25,0:07:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem no matter my efforts,\nyou shall continue to oppose us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are powerless.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack any means of fighting us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But if someone needs my help,\nI refuse to idly stand by.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to prove to them
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.01,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that no matter how bad things get, as long as they\ndon't give up, their voices will reach {\i1}someone{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's simply absurd.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are those girls still alone then?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing else, their voices reached {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just walk away?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their problem. It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, {\i1}why{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.01,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. Why do you refuse?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those girls were in pain this entire time,\nand not a single adult took responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're saying {\i1}you{\i0} will take responsibility?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not your children.\nWhy put the onus on yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not my children.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter happened to bring me to Abydos
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just so happened to meet them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a stranger to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does that matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.20,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are crying for help!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What more do you need?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.00,0:09:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you believe {\i1}this{\i0}\nis how adults bear responsibility? {Oooooof, the intro sequence is back to haunt us. I'm not in love with this, but }
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If they laugh, you laugh with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're sad, you comfort them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're lost, you guide them.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be an adult!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gravely mistaken.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults bend society to their own will.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.27,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They decide what is right, what is proper.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the norm, and what is not.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They wield authority to steer the aimless,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge to control the ignorant,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.40,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and power to rule the weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is what it means to be an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply don't understand. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.83,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have ruled over Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.50,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been yours.\nThe authority, the privileges...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mystics that fill this academy city.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.88,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been brief,\nbut you held it all in the palm of your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you threw it all away\nwithout a moment's hesitation!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth and mystery. Authority. Riches. {\i1}Power{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To throw that all away is madness.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So why {\i1}did{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I told you, you would never understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears we've reached an impasse.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.75,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had high hopes for you, but it appears\nthere's nothing further to discuss.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.96,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find {*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san} in a laboratory\nbeneath one of Kaiser PMC's desert bases.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimesis allowed us to observe\na different facet of Mystics: Terror.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.93,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal was to explore\nits application on a living student.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl was meant to serve\nas a test bed to confirm our hypotheses.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hypotheses?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.19,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that negotiations have broken down,\nmy hands are tied.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regrettable, but our involvement ends here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Hoshino is...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Do what you will.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to take her, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.62,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, assuming the director\nwill allow you to reach her in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we had this conversation.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,May we meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.77,0:11:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A laboratory underneath the Kaiser PMC base...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino's there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they've been holding her captive?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't go in without a plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we even say once we find her?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.17,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, before that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We scold her.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.17,0:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back on her word.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She deserves to be punished.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we scold her
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for her own good. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.23,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find her together and say "welcome home".
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Where did {\i1}that{\i0} corny line come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too sappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It just {\i1}screams{\i0} blue skies, happy memories! {### Reference to the tagline for Blue Archive JP said by the Black Suit VA during all their livestreams, gotta find an equivalent phrase to use here for BDs}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We could never pull that off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.70,0:12:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll say it, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a little embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't catch me dead saying that!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nonomi laugh}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but there's only five of us—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.55,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do this on our own.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to find some allies.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What about PS68?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.39,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They did help us before, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone. It's been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well, Hifumi{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! It was all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.04,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to visit you at your school.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it, where's Hoshino{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the thing is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.01,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed a lot\nsince we last saw each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.93,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wish we'd known sooner\nwhat Hoshino{**-senpai} was going through.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could have stopped her.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.60,0:13:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're here about Hoshino{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. To put it simply,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.65,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd like Trinity's help to save Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.91,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask for your help, {*}Miss Nagisa{*Nagisa-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should I try first?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.09,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This shortcake is rich with cream\nand complements the tea exquisitely.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this Mont Blanc is equally irresistible.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, {*}Miss Nagisa{*Nagisa-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those students from Abydos have helped me before.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So please—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.90,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It would indeed appear that this company,\nKaiser PMC, is a negative influence on our students.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you'll hel—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.83,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,However.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the matter of the Treaty to consider.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot afford to act hastily.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have some time to think this over?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're put on hold, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was hoping this would work.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not going to be that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.60,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding help is a lot tougher than we thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.19,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the next group helping us either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still no reason to give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that the others couldn't attend this meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have liked for Chinatsu{**-san} to attend at least,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but this school has a bit of trouble following the rules.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Chinatsu{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for being late.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.15,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.53,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's mine...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for keeping you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We just managed to finish up—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your break!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's trouble in the cafeteria! {## FUUKA IS BEING KIDNAPPED AGAIN (눈‸눈 )}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.79,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, and thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the mess!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are things always this hectic around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's actually been on the quiet side.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, I wonder how\nthe negotiations are going on their end?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Head Prefect is busy right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back again later.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.07,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get on your knees and lick my feet, maybe I can—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.45,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.83,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you have zero pride as an adult?\nShouldn't you at least hesitate?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He really means it...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Enough! Get off me already!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,P-President Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him. He's on his knees.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation must be quite serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, President Hina...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.19,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not actually kneeling, he's... um...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking... my feet...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.98,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Prefect Team didn't give us an answer, either...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We did everything we could! {Well, HE did what he could... the glorious bastard...}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.29,0:17:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones left are Problem Solver 68.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.59,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they agree to help us?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This one's the one.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what gives?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.85,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the address they gave me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what? You're telling me {\i1}this{\i0} is their office?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a miscommunication?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.98,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only lead we have on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, we came all this way for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did they run off to?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, been a while!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome in!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful stall!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a very nostalgic vibe!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.43,0:18:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, Shiba Seki Ramen started out as just a little stall.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like I'm back in those days, almost.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can have your ramen again.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.02,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I don't know what woulda happened\nif it weren't for that cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would've figured something out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not like quittin' was on the menu anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.28,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still plenty o' folk\nwaitin' to taste my ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, these two darlings stopped by.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.33,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tucked right in, said my ramen\nhit just the spot after a long day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't ask for more than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How're things for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, could be better.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried reaching out to\na lot of people to ask for help.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.01,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're having some trouble\nlocating the last group.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't find them soon,\nwe may have to give up on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, can we get the bill?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.07,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to fight Kaiser PMC for free?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.66,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's in it for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, and I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kayoko{**-chan}. Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.55,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"We don't need your money.\nThis super tasty ramen is all we need!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.97,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's written all over her face!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama} is so brave!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.27,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't waste time with words\nas she marches into hell for a bowl of ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.94,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the picture of a hard-boiled outlaw!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I think it over first?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.03,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.49,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.71,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Hold on, Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't beat yerself up over it, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith that they'll help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Faith, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.18,0:20:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, my restaurant'll always be there\nso long as my customers believe in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same thing 'ere.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.82,0:20:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If everythin' goes wrong,\njust start over and try again.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.07,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There'll always be a path forward,\nas long as you believe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go get 'em, Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And once you're done,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there'll be pipin' hot ramen waiting for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've packed plenty of ammunition.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser PMC doesn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the intel {*}Teacher{*Sensei} got us,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai} is being held in District 51,\nin one of Kaiser PMC's bases.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.24,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our objective is to rescue Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{=5}Let's do this.

